    format("Hive Drone: This area is off-limits to Rangers!\n"),
    format("Hive Drone: No... How could I lose to a Ranger…")
    )
    msgbox(format("Hive Drone: The Seer punish us for this…"), MSGBOX_AUTOCLOSE)
